titles.title: Messiah is the King of kings

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Messiah is the King of kings,
Messiah is the Lord of lords.
Messiah is the King of kings,
Messiah is the Lord of lords.
He is the King of kings,
And the Lord of lords.
Messiah is the King of kings,
Messiah is the Lord of lords.
